description: Frank Gourmet Hot Dogs is a mobile food truck in Buffalo that puts a gourmet twist on an American classic – the hot dog. That's right folks, no dirty water dogs here! Instead, we take the hot dog and do our best to make it better. Using fresh ingredients and a little creative genius, Frank approaches the hot dog in a way that no other casual restaurant or food cart in Buffalo has ever done!  In addition to hot dogs, Frank offers hand-cut fries accompanied with specialty ketchups and aiolis. Our sweet potato fries are kicked up with garlic, cilantro and lime. We also offer a variety of vegetarian options, including homemade veggie dogs.
name: Frank Gourmet Hot Dogs
